000068.title: Fashion Show 97 by Yoko Miki
000068.caption: Fashion Show 97 by Yoko Miki" is a captivating legend of fashion that, whether anchored in historical fact or imaginative narrative, sparks the wonder of what a groundbreaking runway event of the late 1990s could have been. Imagine a visionary designer—Yoko Miki—who dared to blur the lines between the timeless beauty of traditional Japanese aesthetics and the raw, electric energy of modern futurism.
